\begin_layout Standard
一般形式的圈积分，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int\dd^{4}k_{1}\cdots\dd^{4}k_{n}\frac{B}{A_{1}^{m_{1}}A_{1}^{m_{2}}\cdots A_{n}^{m_{n}}}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A_{i}=q_{i}^{2}-m_{i}^{2},
\]

\end_inset

对应费曼图中的一些四动量，
\begin_inset Formula $m_{i}$
\end_inset

是对应的粒子质量。
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

是矢量
\begin_inset Formula $q_{i}$
\end_inset

的一个多项式。根据费曼参数化，把它变成：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\int\dd^{4}k_{1}\cdots\dd^{4}\frac{B}{A_{1}^{m_{1}}A_{1}^{m_{2}}\cdots A_{n}^{m_{n}}} & =\frac{\Gamma\left(m_{1}+\cdots+m_{n}\right)}{\Gamma\left(m_{1}\right)\cdots\Gamma\left(m_{n}\right)}\times\\
 & \int_{0}^{1}\dd x_{1}\cdots\dd x_{n}\delta\left(\sum x_{i}-1\right)\dd^{4}k_{1}\cdots\dd^{4}k_{n}\frac{\prod x_{i}^{m_{i}-1}}{\left[\sum x_{i}A_{i}\right]^{\sum m_{i}}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

分母中的表达式
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}A_{1}+x_{2}A_{2}+\cdots$
\end_inset

是积分变量
\begin_inset Formula $k_{1},k_{2},\cdots$
\end_inset

的二次多项式。通过平移积分变量，可以把
\begin_inset Formula $k_{1},k_{2},\cdots$
\end_inset

的线性项消除，最后我们能得到：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{1}A_{1}+x_{2}A_{2}+\cdots=\varphi+K\left(k_{1}^{\prime},k_{2}^{\prime},\cdots\right).
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

是一个 quadratic form（homogeneous polynomial，
\begin_inset CommandInset href
LatexCommand href
name "Quadratic form"
target "https://handwiki.org/wiki/Quadratic_form#:~:text=Quadratic%20forms%20are%20homogeneous%20quadratic%20polynomials%20in%20n,e%20z%202%20%2B%20f%20x%20z%20%28ternary%29"
literal "false"

\end_inset

）。而
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi$
\end_inset

是矢量
\begin_inset Formula $p_{i}$
\end_inset

的heterogeneous quadratic form，
\begin_inset Formula $p_{i}$
\end_inset

是费曼图的外动量。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
让我们考虑动量
\begin_inset Formula $p_{i}$
\end_inset

的平方以及标量积是实数的情形。容易验证，如果
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi$
\end_inset

的值是正数，则关于
\begin_inset Formula $k_{1},k_{2},\cdots$
\end_inset

 的积分结果是实数（对于旋量函数的情形，结果是自共轭的）。考虑作 Wick 转动：
\color blue

\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\dd k^{0}\,f\left(k^{0}\right) & =i\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\dd k^{0}\,f\left(ik^{0}\right)\\
\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\frac{\dd^{4}k}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{1}{\left(k^{2}-\Delta+i\varepsilon\right)^{n}} & ={\color{red}i\left(-1\right)^{n}}\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\frac{\dd^{4}k_{E}}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{1}{\left(k_{E}^{2}+\Delta-i\varepsilon\right)^{n}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\color inherit
左变量代换
\begin_inset Formula $k_{1}^{0}\to ik_{1}^{\prime0},\cdots$
\end_inset

，容易验证
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

是正定的，由于所有的
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i}$
\end_inset

都是正的。所以若
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi>0$
\end_inset

，对于所有的
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i}$
\end_inset

，则积分是实数。另一方面，如果对于某些
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha_{i}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi<0$
\end_inset

，积分将是复数。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset CommandInset href
LatexCommand href
name "gudrun-loop-into"
target "https://www.ippp.dur.ac.uk/~gudrun/teaching/ILC.pdf"
literal "false"

\end_inset

，朗道奇点就是圈积分的 Cayley matrix 行列式为零的解，满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{cases}
x_{i}\left(q_{i}^{2}-m_{i}^{2}\right)=0 & \forall i\\
\sum_{i=1}^{N}x_{i}q_{i}=0.
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

若对应圈积分所有内线的粒子同时在壳，称为 leading Landau singularity。如果解中部分
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i}=0$
\end_inset

，则对应低阶的 Landau singularity。形如
\begin_inset Formula $1/\varepsilon$
\end_inset

的软和共线（soft and collinear ）singularities 总是来自于某些
\begin_inset Formula $z_{i}=0$
\end_inset

的情况。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
费曼参数化
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
费曼参数化基于一些简单的数学公式。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
最简单的是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{AB}=\int_{0}^{1}\dd x\frac{1}{\left[A+(B-A)x\right]^{2}}=\int_{0}^{1}\dd x\dd y\delta(x+y-1)\frac{1}{\left[xA+yB\right]^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

这个等式可以这么理解，首先从量纲上，右边的积分结果一定是
\begin_inset Formula $A,B$
\end_inset

的负二次方，结果只可能由
\begin_inset Formula $A,B$
\end_inset

和它们的系数组成。积分对
\begin_inset Formula $A,B$
\end_inset

是对称的，所以不可能出现类似
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{A}{B}$
\end_inset

的结构，所以只能是
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{n}{AB}$
\end_inset

，然后考虑系数。首先取
\begin_inset Formula $A=B$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{A^{2}}\int_{0}^{1}\dd{x}\dd{y}\delta\left(x+y-1\right)
\]

\end_inset


\series bold
这种类型的积分需要考虑积分区域的变化，因为
\begin_inset Formula $\delta\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

函数相当于一个分布，使得积分区间中某些区域不贡献了
\series default
。
\begin_inset Formula $\delta\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

函数总是会减少一个维度，因此总相当于积分区域
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

的维度减少，这样我们需要知道降维后的积分区域
\begin_inset Formula $D^{\prime}$
\end_inset

的面积，和相对于原来积分测度的伸缩比例。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
比如在二维情况下，
\begin_inset Formula $\delta\left(x+y-1\right)$
\end_inset

限定积分区域在
\begin_inset Formula $x+y=1$
\end_inset

的一条支线上，这条直线长度为
\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt{2}$
\end_inset

，直线上的点坐标为
\begin_inset Formula $\left(x,1-x\right)$
\end_inset

，所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd{s}=\sqrt{\abs{\frac{\partial x}{\partial x}}^{2}+\abs{\frac{\partial(1-x)}{\partial x}}^{2}}\dd x=\sqrt{2}\dd{x}
\]

\end_inset

与一维的积分测度 
\begin_inset Formula $\dd x=\dd y$
\end_inset

 相比，具有 
\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt{2}$
\end_inset

 因子，因此回到一维时候要乘以 
\begin_inset Formula $1/\sqrt{2}$
\end_inset

，结果为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

，即这条线在 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

轴或 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

 轴的投影为
\begin_inset Formula $(0,1)$
\end_inset

。也就是说，满足条件的二维积分区域对一维的投影长度为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

，所以直接得到积分区域的一维测度为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

。注意这个投影朝原点的方向。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
对于高维的情况，
\begin_inset Formula $\delta\left(x+y+\cdots+z\right)=1$
\end_inset

。总的测度体积是
\begin_inset Formula $1^{n}=1$
\end_inset

。用积分式表示
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

函数的限制，可以写成 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{0}^{1}\dd{x}\int_{0}^{1}\dd{y}\cdots\int_{0}^{1}\dd{z}\delta\left(x+y+\cdots+z\right)\to\int_{0}^{1}\dd{x}\int_{0}^{1-x}\dd{y}\int_{0}^{1-x-y}\cdots\int_{0}^{1-x-y\cdots}\dd{z}
\]

\end_inset

其中考虑了
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x+y\le1,\quad x+y+z\le1,\quad\cdots
\]

\end_inset

这个积分表示的是
\begin_inset Formula $n-1$
\end_inset

维单位锥体的体积（各边都相等），
\begin_inset Formula $V=\frac{1}{\left(n-1\right)!}$
\end_inset

。再类似上面，推测一般情况下有：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{A_{1}A_{2}\cdots A_{n}}=\int_{0}^{1}\dd{x_{1}}\cdots\int_{0}^{1}\dd{x_{n}}\delta\left(\sum x_{i}-1\right)\frac{\left(n-1\right)!}{\left[x_{1}A_{1}+\cdots+x_{n}A_{n}\right]^{n}}
\]

\end_inset

类似地，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{AB^{n}}=\int_{0}^{1}\cdots\int_{0}^{1}\dd x\dd y\delta\left(x+y-1\right)\frac{ny^{n-1}}{\left[xA+yB\right]^{n+1}}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{ABC}=\int_{0}^{1}\dd x\dd y\dd z\delta\left(x+y+z-1\right)\frac{2}{\left[xA+yB+zC\right]^{3}}
\]

\end_inset

通过这些公式，可以把传播子合并起来，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\int\frac{\dd^{4}k}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{1}{k^{2}}\frac{1}{\left(k-p\right)^{2}} & =\int\frac{\dd^{4}k}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\int_{0}^{1}\dd x\frac{1}{\left[k^{2}+x\left(\left(k-p\right)^{2}-k^{2}\right)\right]^{2}}\\
 & =\int\frac{\dd^{4}k}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\int_{0}^{1}\dd x\frac{1}{\left[k^{2}-2kxp+xp^{2}\right]^{2}}\\
 & =\int_{0}^{1}\dd x\int\frac{\dd^{4}k}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{1}{\left[\left(k-xp\right)^{2}-\Delta\right]^{2}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta=-p^{2}x(1-x)$
\end_inset

。我们可以通过平移 
\begin_inset Formula $k\to k+xp$
\end_inset

使积分只依赖于
\begin_inset Formula $k^{2}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
Peskin书给出了更一般的形式，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{A_{1}^{m_{1}}A_{1}^{m_{2}}A_{n}^{m_{n}}}=\int_{0}^{1}\dd x_{1}\cdots\dd x_{n}\delta\left(\sum x_{i}-1\right)\frac{\prod x_{i}^{m_{i}-1}}{\left[\sum x_{i}A_{i}\right]^{\sum m_{i}}}\frac{\Gamma\left(m_{1}+\cdots+m_{n}\right)}{\Gamma\left(m_{1}\right)\cdots\Gamma\left(m_{n}\right)}
\]

\end_inset

对积分上限可以做更加细致的处理，例如：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \int_{0}^{1}\dd{x}\int_{0}^{1}\dd{y}\int_{0}^{1}\dd{z}\delta\left(1-x-y-z\right)\\
\text{考虑不等式约束}\Rightarrow & \left.\int_{0}^{1}\dd{x}\int_{0}^{1-x}\dd{y}\right|_{z=1-x-y}\\
(x\leftrightarrow1-x)\Rightarrow & \left.\int_{0}^{1}\dd{x}\int_{0}^{x}\dd{y}\right|_{z=x-y}\\
(y\leftrightarrow x-y)\Rightarrow & \left.\int_{0}^{1}\dd{x}\int_{0}^{x}\dd{y}\right|_{z=y}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
类似地，一般情况下可写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{A_{1}^{m_{1}}A_{1}^{m_{2}}A_{n}^{m_{n}}}=\int_{0}^{1}{\color{blue}\dd{x_{1}}}\int_{0}^{x_{1}}{\color{blue}\dd{x_{2}}}\cdots\int_{0}^{x_{n-2}}{\color{blue}\dd x_{n-1}}\frac{\prod{\color{blue}y_{i}^{m_{i}-1}}}{\left[\sum{\color{blue}y_{i}}A_{i}\right]^{\sum m_{i}}}\frac{\Gamma\left(m_{1}+\cdots+m_{n}\right)}{\Gamma\left(m_{1}\right)\cdots\Gamma\left(m_{n}\right)}
\]

\end_inset

注意，被积式中已经去掉了
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

函数，并且
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

个独立传播子只需 
\begin_inset Formula $n-1$
\end_inset

 个费曼参数。其中：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
y_{1}= & 1-x_{1}\\
y_{2}= & \hspace{4ex}x_{1}-x_{2}\\
y_{3}= & \hspace{9ex}x_{2}-x_{3}\\
\cdots= & \cdots\\
y_{n-1}= & \hspace{14ex}x_{n-2}-x_{n-1}\\
y_{n}= & \hspace{21ex}x_{n-1}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
应用到特定情形，例如：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{A^{\alpha}B^{\beta}}=\int_{0}^{1}\dd z\frac{w^{\alpha-1}\left(1-w\right)^{\beta-1}}{\left[wA+\left(1-w\right)B\right]^{\alpha+\beta}}\frac{\Gamma\left(\alpha+\beta\right)}{\Gamma\left(\alpha\right)\Gamma\left(\beta\right)}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
通过变量代换：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
z\equiv\frac{wA}{wA+\left(1-w\right)B},\quad\left(1-z\right)=\frac{\left(1-w\right)B}{wA+\left(1-w\right)B},\quad\dd{z}=\frac{AB\dd{w}}{\left[wA+\left(1-w\right)B\right]^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{0}^{1}\dd w\frac{w^{\alpha-1}\left(1-w\right)^{\beta-1}}{\left[wA+\left(1-w\right)B\right]^{\alpha+\beta}}=\frac{1}{A^{\alpha}B^{\beta}}\int_{0}^{1}\dd z\,z^{\alpha-1}\left(1-z\right)^{\beta-1}=\frac{1}{A^{\alpha}B^{\beta}}B\left(\alpha,\beta\right)
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $B\left(\alpha,\beta\right)$
\end_inset

 是 beta function.
 一般的式子可以用归纳法推导。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
积分区域
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
费曼参数化在几何上对应单形，即
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

维空间中给定点的凸组合（convex combinations）
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\{ \lambda_{1}p_{1}+\cdots\lambda_{k}p_{k}|\lambda_{i}\ge0\wedge\lambda_{1}+\cdots+\lambda_{k}=1\right\} .
\]

\end_inset

几何区域是
\begin_inset Formula $k-1$
\end_inset

维的，若
\begin_inset Formula $p_{i}\in\symbb R^{n}$
\end_inset

并仿射独立（affinely independent）且
\begin_inset Formula $n\ge k-1$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
具体来说，积分区域
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{0}^{1}{\color{blue}\dd{x_{1}}}\int_{0}^{x_{1}}{\color{blue}\dd{x_{2}}}\cdots\int_{0}^{x_{n-2}}{\color{blue}\dd x_{n-1}}$
\end_inset

是高维空间中的棱锥（pyramid）
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & 0\le x_{1}\le1,\quad0\le x_{2}\le x_{1},\quad0\le x_{n-2}\le x_{n-1}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

容易知道，积分区域包括的点有：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(1,1,\cdots,1\right),\quad\left(1,1,\cdots,0\right),\quad\left(1,0,\cdots,0\right),\quad\left(0,0,\cdots,0\right)
\]

\end_inset

对于单形，只需知道这些边界上的点，就可以确定此几何区域。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Schwinger 参数化
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
当
\begin_inset Formula $\Im A>0$
\end_inset

时：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{i}{A}=\int_{0}^{\infty}\dd{s}e^{isA}\label{eq:b.5}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\Im A>0$
\end_inset

可以保证积分是良好定义的。
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\frac{i}{A}\right)^{2}=\int_{0}^{\infty}se^{isA}\dd s
\]

\end_inset

可以通过持续求导得到更多等式，例如求导
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

次的结果是：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \frac{i\left(-1\right)^{n-1}\left(n-1\right)!}{A^{n}}=\int_{0}^{\infty}\dd\alpha\left(i\alpha\right)^{n-1}e^{i\alpha A}\\
 & \frac{1}{A^{n}}=\frac{\left(-i\right)^{n}}{\Gamma\left(n\right)!}\int_{0}^{\infty}\dd\alpha\,\alpha^{n-1}e^{i\alpha A}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:b.5"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 暗示了
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{1}{AB}=-\int_{0}^{\infty}\dd s\int_{0}^{\infty}\dd te^{isA+itB}\label{eq:b.7}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $\Im A>0$
\end_inset

 和 
\begin_inset Formula $\Im B>0$
\end_inset

(也就是用费曼传播子)。Schwinger 参数 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 具有很好的物理解释：
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 是 proper times of the particles as they travel along their paths in the
 Feynman graph。Schwinger proper-time interpretation 见 Chapter 32。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
注意如果令
\begin_inset Formula $s+t=\tau$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $x=\frac{t}{s+t}$
\end_inset

，或 
\begin_inset Formula $t=x\tau$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $s=\left(1-x\right)\tau$
\end_inset

，Eq.
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:b.7"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

变成
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\frac{1}{AB} & =-\int_{0}^{\infty}\tau\dd\tau\int_{0}^{1}\dd xe^{i\tau\left(A+Bx-Ax\right)}\\
 & =\int_{0}^{1}\dd x\frac{1}{\left[A+\left(B-A\right)x\right]^{2}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

所以费曼参数化
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

