\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我们经常会遇到分子中带动量因子的积分，比如
\begin_inset Formula $k^{\mu}k^{\nu}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F^{\mu\nu}\left(\Delta\right)=\int\frac{\dd[4]{k}}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\frac{k^{\mu}k^{\nu}}{\left(k^{2}-\Delta\right)^{n}}
\]

\end_inset

可以使用技巧化简它。由于积分是 Lorentz 变换下的张量，积分完它只能是标量 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta$
\end_inset

 的函数；在张量基的角度，它只能依赖于唯一可用的张量
\begin_inset Formula $g^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

。那么仅仅由量纲分析就能知道，把
\begin_inset Formula $k^{\mu}k^{\nu}$
\end_inset

换成
\begin_inset Formula $ck^{2}g^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

，积分的结果相同，对于特定的数
\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

。与
\begin_inset Formula $g^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

进行收缩得到
\begin_inset Formula $c=\frac{1}{4}$
\end_inset

 ，或者一般的
\begin_inset Formula $c=\frac{1}{d}$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\int\frac{\dd[d]{k}}{\left(2\pi\right)^{d}}\frac{k^{\mu}k^{\nu}}{\left(k^{2}-\Delta\right)^{n}} & =cg^{\mu\nu}\int\frac{\dd[d]{k}}{\left(2\pi\right)^{d}}\frac{k^{2}}{\left(k^{2}-\Delta\right)^{n}}\\
\Rightarrow\int\frac{\dd[d]{k}}{\left(2\pi\right)^{d}}\frac{k^{2}}{\left(k^{2}-\Delta\right)^{n}} & =cd\int\frac{\dd[d]{k}}{\left(2\pi\right)^{d}}\frac{k^{2}}{\left(k^{2}-\Delta\right)^{n}}\quad\Rightarrow cd=1
\end{align*}

\end_inset

立得：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int\frac{\dd[d]{k}}{\left(2\pi\right)^{d}}\frac{k^{\mu}k^{\nu}}{\left(k^{2}-\Delta\right)^{n}}=\frac{1}{d}g^{\mu\nu}\int\frac{\dd[d]{k}}{\left(2\pi\right)^{d}}\frac{k^{2}}{\left(k^{2}-\Delta\right)^{n}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

